<div class="space-y-4">
  <div class="grid gap-3">
    <div class="rounded-[24px] border border-black/10 bg-white px-4 py-3">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-black/45">Tên</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-black"><%= credentials[:name].presence || '-' %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-[24px] border border-black/10 bg-white px-4 py-3">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-black/45">Email</p>
      <p class="mt-2 break-all text-sm font-semibold text-black"><%= credentials[:email] %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-[24px] border border-primary-200 bg-primary-50 px-4 py-3" data-controller="clipboard" data-clipboard-text-value="<%= credentials[:password] %>">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary-700">Mật khẩu</p>
      <div class="mt-2 flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
        <p class="break-all font-mono text-base font-semibold text-primary-900"><%= credentials[:password] %></p>

        <button
          type="button"
          class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-full border-0 bg-transparent text-primary-700 transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-primary-200 hover:text-primary-950 active:scale-95 focus:outline-none"
          data-action="click->clipboard#copy"
          aria-label="Copy mật khẩu"
          title="Copy mật khẩu"
        >
          <span data-clipboard-target="defaultIcon">
            <%= lucide_icon('copy', class: 'h-4 w-4', "aria-hidden": true) %>
          </span>
          <span class="hidden" data-clipboard-target="successIcon">
            <%= lucide_icon('check', class: 'h-4 w-4', "aria-hidden": true) %>
          </span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm leading-6 text-amber-900">
    Mật khẩu chỉ hiển thị một lần duy nhất. Hãy lưu lại thông tin đăng nhập trước khi đóng modal này.
  </div>

  <div class="flex justify-end">
    <button
      type="button"
      class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-2xl border border-primary-500 bg-primary-500 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:border-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-600 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-200 focus:ring-offset-2"
      data-action="modal#close"
    >
      Tôi đã lưu lại
    </button>
  </div>
</div>
